508
509const RISCVVIntrinsicInfo *getRISCVVIntrinsicInfo(unsigned IntrinsicID) {
510 struct KeyType {
511 unsigned IntrinsicID;
512 };
513 KeyType Key = {IntrinsicID};
514 auto Table = makeArrayRef(RISCVVIntrinsicsTable);
515 auto Idx = std::lower_bound(Table.begin(), Table.end(), Key,
516 [](const RISCVVIntrinsicInfo &LHS, const KeyType &RHS) {
517 if (LHS.IntrinsicID < RHS.IntrinsicID)
518 return true;
519 if (LHS.IntrinsicID > RHS.IntrinsicID)
520 return false;
521 return false;
522 });
523
524 if (Idx == Table.end() ||
525 Key.IntrinsicID != Idx->IntrinsicID)
526 return nullptr;
527 return &*Idx;
528}
529#endif

14410
14411const PseudoInfo *getPseudoInfo(unsigned Pseudo) {
14412 struct KeyType {
14413 unsigned Pseudo;
14414 };
14415 KeyType Key = {Pseudo};
14416 auto Table = makeArrayRef(RISCVVPseudosTable);
14417 auto Idx = std::lower_bound(Table.begin(), Table.end(), Key,
14418 [](const PseudoInfo &LHS, const KeyType &RHS) {
14419 if (LHS.Pseudo < RHS.Pseudo)
14420 return true;
14421 if (LHS.Pseudo > RHS.Pseudo)
14422 return false;
14423 return false;
14424 });
14425
14426 if (Idx == Table.end() ||
14427 Key.Pseudo != Idx->Pseudo)
14428 return nullptr;
14429 return &*Idx;
14430}
14431#endif

20932
20933const RISCVZvlsseg *getPseudo(unsigned IntrinsicID, uint16_t SEW, uint8_t LMUL, uint8_t IndexLMUL) {
20934 struct KeyType {
20935 unsigned IntrinsicID;
20936 uint16_t SEW;
20937 uint8_t LMUL;
20938 uint8_t IndexLMUL;
20939 };
20940 KeyType Key = {IntrinsicID, SEW, LMUL, IndexLMUL};
20941 auto Table = makeArrayRef(RISCVZvlssegTable);
20942 auto Idx = std::lower_bound(Table.begin(), Table.end(), Key,
20943 [](const RISCVZvlsseg &LHS, const KeyType &RHS) {
20944 if (LHS.IntrinsicID < RHS.IntrinsicID)
20945 return true;
20946 if (LHS.IntrinsicID > RHS.IntrinsicID)
20947 return false;
20948 if (LHS.SEW < RHS.SEW)
20949 return true;
20950 if (LHS.SEW > RHS.SEW)
20951 return false;
20952 if (LHS.LMUL < RHS.LMUL)
20953 return true;
20954 if (LHS.LMUL > RHS.LMUL)
20955 return false;
20956 if (LHS.IndexLMUL < RHS.IndexLMUL)
20957 return true;
20958 if (LHS.IndexLMUL > RHS.IndexLMUL)
20959 return false;
20960 return false;
20961 });
20962
20963 if (Idx == Table.end() ||
20964 Key.IntrinsicID != Idx->IntrinsicID ||
20965 Key.SEW != Idx->SEW ||
20966 Key.LMUL != Idx->LMUL ||
20967 Key.IndexLMUL != Idx->IndexLMUL)
20968 return nullptr;
20969 return &*Idx;
20970}
20971#endif

21212const SysReg *lookupSysRegByEncoding(uint16_t Encoding) {
21213 struct KeyType {
21214 uint16_t Encoding;
21215 };
21216 KeyType Key = {Encoding};
21217 auto Table = makeArrayRef(SysRegsList);
21218 auto Idx = std::lower_bound(Table.begin(), Table.end(), Key,
21219 [](const SysReg &LHS, const KeyType &RHS) {
21220 if (LHS.Encoding < RHS.Encoding)
21221 return true;
21222 if (LHS.Encoding > RHS.Encoding)
21223 return false;
21224 return false;
21225 });
21226
21227 if (Idx == Table.end() ||
21228 Key.Encoding != Idx->Encoding)
21229 return nullptr;
21230 return &*Idx;
21231}
